# Migrations live here, one timestamped .sql file each.
#
# Create one with `supabase migration new <name>`, apply it locally with
# `supabase db reset`, and never edit a migration that has been applied to a
# deployed database — write a follow-up instead.
#
# The schema itself lands in a later slice (see the data model section of the
# MVP build spec). This directory exists so the first migration has a home.
